location.fullValue: Coral II Plan, Banning Lewis Ranch

data.description: Immaculately maintained 3 story home in the desirable Banning Lewis Ranch Community that shows like a model!    The entry level has a versatile flex space that can be used as a living area, office, playroom, workout room, mudroom, or so much more.  The second main level boasts a modern open floor plan with the kitchen, living room, 2 bedrooms, and a full bath. The deck wraps the second level to enjoy the beautiful Colorado views. The spacious primary suite with ensuite bathroom and large walk in closet are on the private third level with its own separate huge living space which has endless possibilities.  This like new home features many designer features and upgrades, upgraded carpet, granite, stainless steel appliances, epoxy garage floor, upgraded cordless blinds, and more!  A fenced side yard offers a bit of privacy. Banning Lewis Ranch is a one of a kind community which offers a full rec center, pools, splash parks, workout center, 65 acres of parks and trails, summer concerts and activities, award winning schools, Close proximity to shops, dining, entertainment, military institutions, and so much more! This home is truly a must see!
